job.title: IIT Madras Executive  Recruitment 2021   Apply online for Various Vacancies in Madras
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the vacancies:

  • Executive Secretary

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by the Indian Institute of Technology Madras for the vacancies of Executive Secretary. If you are finding a government job in Chennai then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Chennai, from 17.05.2021, and till 27.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Chennai and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification to apply for IIT Madras Executive Secretary vacancies in Chennai:

  • To apply for an Executive Secretary vacancies in Chennai, your Degree, Post-graduate  must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 17.05.2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 27.05.2021.

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 37  years old. 

IIT Madras Executive Secretary Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 30.,000-50,000 per month.

How to apply for IIT Madras Executive Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Chennai. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of IIT Madras and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY IIT Madras 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
